Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能和夢中的人說話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是與黑暗的國度對話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那以後好像已經過去了一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個村子的其他人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會告訴你的  全部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉唉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是水脈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下田地就能灌溉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金的夢又實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去通知村裡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裡大家的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  時不時送點東西來也不算壞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是感謝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  楊梅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預知實現的次數增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那個蟲師說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信他嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蟲子讓我看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  假如
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如那是真的的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些藥我會喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西邊的山崖塌方了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有預言的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  不知道該怎樣感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鵑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不時會感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當夢見的東西在現實中發生時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是按照我的想法實現的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是上次的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  也為我們做一個好夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈…別說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再次期待著你的夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是你為了幫助大家才有預知的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是因為託你的福大家才得到幸福嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼好害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然妻子這樣說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我對預知的恐懼沒有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐漸的就把藥喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是海嘯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眉…眉她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種夢一次都沒有夢到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的大災難就一點也預測不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為愚蠢地喝了藥才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才沒能救到眉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我停止了喝藥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後  預知的次數在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內容也越來越準確了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在門口發現的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打起精神啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了夢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多的汗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的夢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是身體不舒服而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鵑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢中看到的那種病
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從指尖開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到胳膊都發青
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擴散到全身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像泥塊一樣崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮上只有我一個人活了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過你叫銀古吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那夢境成為現實的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候  你騙了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我體內的不是帶來預知夢的蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:11:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是將我夢中所見到的東西轉化成現實的蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種青色的怪病
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從我身邊的人開始發作的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄰居…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直蔓延開去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那簡直就是夢境的重現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在為止我做的全部預言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的夢境造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要騙我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我無法根除這種蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被寄生了要到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不傷害宿主的話只能讓二者共生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果直接說出蟲的真面目的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿主可能會承受不了而崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既…既然那樣的話我死就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我那種謊言…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼讓我活下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已經變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何我都會找到對付這種蟲的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢野間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棲息在宿主夢中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候會從夢中出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們就成為可將夢轉成現實的媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些沒成真的夢並非無法轉為現實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是隨著它們的增多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從夢中出來的次數就越來越多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後被實現的範圍和規模也越來越大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  蟲的實體曬到陽光就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很脆弱的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道它們是怎麼到現實世界來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子們一定隱藏在某個地方讓夢不斷延續
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當宿主醒來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子們又在那裡沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能找到這個地方的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種規模的「夢現」先前也沒有記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種藥的話阻止不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是增加藥的用量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都喝了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅持住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿解毒劑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了  我不該活在這世上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼球在動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始做夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢話？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你的過錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是蟲的過錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙方都只是為了生存
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有做錯什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大雁嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是夢話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點邏輯也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在到底在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一片蘆葦塘中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種耳鳴？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為剛才的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的夢轉換成現實了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來像是大雁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些全部都是夢野間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎您回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鵑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對不起你們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定在恨我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你們和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了  金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有做錯什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏風上好象有什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示著的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的夢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢是從枕邊出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去打水…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢是通過枕頭出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子們隱藏的某個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當宿主醒來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子們又在那裡沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的蟲子們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧做了應急處理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣好像已經得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成這樣  你知道是怎麼回事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是砍了枕頭一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.29,0:20:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「枕頭」這個詞彙源自「魂居之處」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經有「魂居之處」之說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人活著有三分之一的時間要和枕頭接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人認為那是人的魂魄所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那裡也就成了夢野間的巢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接夢和現實的通道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀壞枕頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就等於傷害你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢和現實之間是魂居之所
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰能通過這個地方的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能夢見那個禁斷的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人又再次做起了磨刀師的老本行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們都說他手藝很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他心裡好像有什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候突然來回揮舞著刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後把刀鋒刺向了自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.68,0:21:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人很懼怕睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕睡著的時候自己的靈魂不知道會去了哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從那個男人斬了枕頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再沒有做過夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}「遊蕩的沼澤」


